{
  "stem": "27507.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And there, of course, there was smuggling that was smuggling on the smaller scale, the children, individually.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "There was smuggling then on a bigger scale and there were groups of smugglers--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--grown-ups which would arrange between-- to smuggle bigger amounts of stuff, like sacks of food, of flour, of some kind of cereal, of sugar to be thrown over the wall.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there would be Jewish smugglers--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--who would collect it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One must say here that there was a large underworld in Poland in Warsaw, and the underworld was-- there was some Jewish underworld as well.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Jewish underworld and the Polish underworld were--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--were cooperating.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had good connection.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So as long as it was organized, as long as the Polish underworld would get paid, they were quite prepared to cooperate and to help in bringing those food supplies.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there were some-- there were much bigger food supplies.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were food supplies which were coming in lorries or in hole or in a huge horse-drawn carts.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was organized then with full knowledge of the gendarme on the [NON-ENGLISH], who would be paid, of course.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then they would bribed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everybody was bribed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Everybody was-- was-- knew about it very well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they would bring almost officially a whole-- whole wagons of supplies into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there were of course people in the ghetto who were-- as for the social differences, there were the majority was poor, and a large amount was desperately poor.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But there were people who were well off.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were people who were rich.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
